data.description: Beautiful Country Property on a little over 3 Unrestricted Acres located in HARDIN ISD; Quick access to HWY 105 for traveling to Beaumont or Cleveland.  The Home is a 3/2 "Palm Harbor" with an Open Concept, Mock Fireplace and Large Living Room that can be a Flex Area.  Outside features a Large Covered Back Porch which is great for enjoying a glass of sweet tea during the day or watching the stars at night; back and sides are fenced with PLENTY of room for a pool, shop, RV parking and outdoor activities.  Per sellers, No Flooding.
